            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New</h2>

<ul>
<li>Meeting recording with speaker diarisation (for @Simon)</li>
<li>thinkur MCP — let Claude, ChatGPT, and Cursor talk to your speech data</li>
<li>Free tier — try thinkur without a license</li>
<li>Reliable multi-key hotkeys</li>
<li>Dropped minimum to macOS 15.0 (for @super_bavario)</li>
<li>Bug fixes (thanks @johnway___, @fhreire)</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
