            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New</h2>

<ul>
<li><strong>Faster, more accurate transcription</strong> — upgraded to an improved, lighter speech model</li>
<li><strong>Better UX</strong> — prettier in some areas</li>
<li><strong>In-app checkout</strong> — purchase flow now opens directly in the app</li>
<li><strong>Clearer pricing page</strong> — updated for clarity</li>
</ul>

<h2>Fixes</h2>

<ul>
<li>Fixed bottom bar positioning (requested by @eddie_08)</li>
<li>Fixed window close behavior (requested by @johnway___)</li>
<li>Improved permission flow with better error handling</li>
<li>License activation improvements (requested by @johnway___)</li>
<li>Show-in-dock setting + menu bar improvements</li>
<li>Music dimming while recording is auto-enabled</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
